text:
🌳🌿Diversity Trail is among 1 of the 3 Trails at the Tampines Eco Green.
🦅🐢🐿️🦎The scenic Diversity Trail is well shaded and peaceful with diverse landscape that includes freshwater ponds, open grassland and snags.
🦜🐦‍⬛Visitors would also come across Bird Hides that are strategically located along the Trail.
